---
title: Garlicky Tofu Feta Fusilli Pasta  with Olives
description: This creamy, garlicky Mediterranean tofu pasta is packed to the brim with flavour! Juicy tomatoes, briny olives and salty feta will have you dreaming of the Grecian coast.
